#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:6
msgid "Built-in Functions"
msgstr "內建函數"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:8
msgid ""
"Vyper provides a collection of built-in functions available in the global "
"namespace of all contracts."
msgstr "Vyper 提供了一組內建函數，可在所有合約的全域命名空間中使用。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:11
msgid "Bitwise Operations"
msgstr "位元運算"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:16
msgid ""
"Return ``x`` with the bits shifted ``_shift`` places. A positive ``_shift`` "
"value equals a left shift, a negative value is a right shift."
msgstr ""
"回傳 ``x`` 將其位元移位 ``_shift`` 個位置。正 ``_shift`` 值表示左移，負值表示"
"右移。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:18
msgid ""
"@external\n"
"@view\n"
"def foo(x: uint256, y: int128) -> uint256:\n"
"    return shift(x, y)"
msgstr ""
"@external\n"
"@view\n"
"def foo(x: uint256, y: int128) -> uint256:\n"
"    return shift(x, y)"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:25
msgid ""
">>> ExampleContract.foo(2, 8)\n"
"512"
msgstr ""
">>> ExampleContract.foo(2, 8)\n"
"512"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:32
msgid ""
"This function has been deprecated from version 0.3.8 onwards. Please use the "
"``<<`` and ``>>`` operators instead."
msgstr "此函數自 0.3.8 版起已被棄用。請改用 ``<<`` 和 ``>>`` 運算子。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:36
msgid ""
"The functions ``bitwise_and``, ``bitwise_or``, ``bitwise_xor`` and "
"``bitwise_not`` have been deprecated from version 0.3.4., and removed in "
"version 0.4.2. Please use their operator versions instead: ``&``, ``|``, "
"``^``, ``~``."
msgstr ""
"函數 ``bitwise_and``、``bitwise_or``、``bitwise_xor`` 和 ``bitwise_not`` 自 "
"0.3.4 版起已被棄用，並在 0.4.2 版中移除。請改用其運算子版本：``&``、``|``、"
"``^``、``~``。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:40
msgid "Chain Interaction"
msgstr "鏈互動"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:43
msgid ""
"Vyper has four built-ins for contract creation; the first three contract "
"creation built-ins rely on the code to deploy already being stored on-chain, "
"but differ in call vs deploy overhead, and whether or not they invoke the "
"constructor of the contract to be deployed. The following list provides a "
"short summary of the differences between them."
msgstr ""
"Vyper 有四個用於合約建立的內建函數；前三個合約建立內建函數依賴已儲存在鏈上的"
"程式碼來部署，但在呼叫與部署的開銷、以及是否呼叫要部署合約的建構函數方面有所"
"不同。以下列表簡要總結了它們之間的差異。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:48
msgid "``create_minimal_proxy_to(target: address, ...)``"
msgstr "``create_minimal_proxy_to(target: address, ...)``"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:46
msgid "Creates an immutable proxy to ``target``"
msgstr "建立一個指向 ``target`` 的不可變代理"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:47
msgid ""
"Expensive to call (incurs a single ``DELEGATECALL`` overhead on every "
"invocation), cheap to create (since it only deploys ``EIP-1167`` forwarder "
"bytecode)"
msgstr ""
"呼叫成本高（每次呼叫都會產生一次 ``DELEGATECALL`` 開銷），建立成本低（因為只"
"部署 ``EIP-1167`` 轉發器位元組碼）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:48 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:53
msgid "Does not have the ability to call a constructor"
msgstr "無法呼叫建構函數"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:49
msgid ""
"Does **not** check that there is code at ``target`` (allows one to deploy "
"proxies counterfactually)"
msgstr "**不**檢查 ``target`` 處是否有程式碼（允許反事實地部署代理）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:53
msgid "``create_copy_of(target: address, ...)``"
msgstr "``create_copy_of(target: address, ...)``"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:51
msgid "Creates a byte-for-byte copy of runtime code stored at ``target``"
msgstr "建立 ``target`` 處儲存的執行時期程式碼的逐位元組副本"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:52 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:57
msgid ""
"Cheap to call (no ``DELEGATECALL`` overhead), expensive to create (200 gas "
"per deployed byte)"
msgstr ""
"呼叫成本低（無 ``DELEGATECALL`` 開銷），建立成本高（每部署一個位元組 200 "
"gas）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:54 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:59
msgid "Performs an ``EXTCODESIZE`` check to check there is code at ``target``"
msgstr "執行 ``EXTCODESIZE`` 檢查以確認 ``target`` 處有程式碼"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:58
msgid "``create_from_blueprint(target: address, ...)``"
msgstr "``create_from_blueprint(target: address, ...)``"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:56
msgid "Deploys a contract using the initcode stored at ``target``"
msgstr "使用儲存在 ``target`` 的 initcode 來部署合約"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:58
msgid ""
"Invokes constructor, requires a special \"blueprint\" contract to be deployed"
msgstr "呼叫建構函數，需要部署一個特殊的「藍圖」合約"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:61
msgid "``raw_create(initcode: Bytes[...], ...)```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:61
msgid ""
"Low-level create. Takes the given initcode, along with the arguments to be "
"abi-encoded, and deploys the initcode after concatenating the abi-encoded "
"arguments."
msgstr ""
"低階建立。接受給定的 initcode 以及要進行 ABI 編碼的引數，並在串接 ABI 編碼後"
"的引數之後部署 initcode。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:65
msgid ""
"Deploys a small, EIP1167-compliant \"minimal proxy contract\" that "
"duplicates the logic of the contract at ``target``, but has its own state "
"since every call to ``target`` is made using ``DELEGATECALL`` to ``target``. "
"To the end user, this should be indistinguishable from an independently "
"deployed contract with the same code as ``target``."
msgstr ""
"部署一個小型、符合 EIP1167 的「最小代理合約」，該合約複製 ``target`` 處合約的"
"邏輯，但擁有自己的狀態，因為對 ``target`` 的每次呼叫都是透過 "
"``DELEGATECALL`` 對 ``target`` 進行的。對終端使用者而言，這應該與具有相同程式"
"碼的獨立部署合約無法區分。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:68
msgid "``target``: Address of the contract to proxy to"
msgstr "``target``：要代理到的合約位址"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:69 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:99
#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:122 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:163
msgid ""
"``value``: The wei value to send to the new contract address (Optional, "
"default 0)"
msgstr "``value``：要發送到新合約位址的 wei 值（選用，默認 0）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:70 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:100
#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:125 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:165
msgid ""
"``revert_on_failure``: If ``False``, instead of reverting when the create "
"operation fails, return the zero address (Optional, default ``True``)"
msgstr ""
"``revert_on_failure``：如果為 ``False``，則在建立操作失敗時不回退，而是回傳零"
"位址（選用，默認 ``True``）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:71 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:101
#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:126 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:166
msgid ""
"``salt``: A ``bytes32`` value utilized by the deterministic ``CREATE2`` "
"opcode (Optional, if not supplied, ``CREATE`` is used)"
msgstr ""
"``salt``：用於確定性 ``CREATE2`` 操作碼的 ``bytes32`` 值（選用，如果未提供則"
"使用 ``CREATE``）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:73
msgid ""
"Returns the address of the newly created proxy contract. If the create "
"operation fails (for instance, in the case of a ``CREATE2`` collision), "
"execution will revert."
msgstr ""
"回傳新建立的代理合約的位址。如果建立操作失敗（例如在 ``CREATE2`` 衝突的情況"
"下），執行將會還原。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:75
msgid ""
"@external\n"
"def foo(target: address) -> address:\n"
"    return create_minimal_proxy_to(target)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:83
msgid ""
"It is very important that the deployed contract at ``target`` is code you "
"know and trust, and does not implement the ``selfdestruct`` opcode or have "
"upgradeable code as this will affect the operation of the proxy contract."
msgstr ""
"非常重要的是，``target`` 處部署的合約必須是你了解且信任的程式碼，並且不實作 "
"``selfdestruct`` 操作碼或具有可升級的程式碼，因為這將影響代理合約的操作。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:87
msgid ""
"There is no runtime check that there is code already deployed at ``target`` "
"(since a proxy may be deployed counterfactually). Most applications may want "
"to insert this check."
msgstr ""
"沒有執行時期檢查來確認 ``target`` 處是否已部署程式碼（因為代理可能是反事實部"
"署的）。大多數應用程式可能希望加入此檢查。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:91
msgid "Before version 0.3.4, this function was named ``create_forwarder_to``."
msgstr "在 0.3.4 版之前，此函數名為 ``create_forwarder_to``。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:96
msgid ""
"Create a physical copy of the runtime code at ``target``. The code at "
"``target`` is byte-for-byte copied into a newly deployed contract."
msgstr ""
"建立 ``target`` 處執行時期程式碼的實體副本。``target`` 處的程式碼會逐位元組複"
"製到新部署的合約中。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:98
msgid "``target``: Address of the contract to copy"
msgstr "``target``：要複製的合約位址"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:103
msgid ""
"Returns the address of the created contract. If the create operation fails "
"(for instance, in the case of a ``CREATE2`` collision), execution will "
"revert. If there is no code at ``target``, execution will revert."
msgstr ""
"回傳建立的合約的位址。如果建立操作失敗（例如在 ``CREATE2`` 衝突的情況下），執"
"行將會還原。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:105
msgid ""
"@external\n"
"def foo(target: address) -> address:\n"
"    return create_copy_of(target)"
msgstr ""
"@external\n"
"def foo(target: address) -> address:\n"
"    return create_copy_of(target)"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:113
msgid ""
"The implementation of ``create_copy_of`` assumes that the code at ``target`` "
"is smaller than 16MB. While this is much larger than the EIP-170 constraint "
"of 24KB, it is a conservative size limit intended to future-proof deployer "
"contracts in case the EIP-170 constraint is lifted. If the code at "
"``target`` is larger than 16MB, the behavior of ``create_copy_of`` is "
"undefined."
msgstr ""
"``create_copy_of`` 的實作假設 ``target`` 處的程式碼小於 16MB。雖然這遠大於 "
"EIP-170 的 24KB 約束，但這是一個保守的大小限制，旨在為部署者合約提供未來保"
"障，以防 EIP-170 約束被取消。如果 ``target`` 處的程式碼大於 16MB，"
"``create_copy_of`` 的行為是未定義的。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:118
msgid ""
"Copy the code of ``target`` into memory and execute it as initcode. In other "
"words, this operation interprets the code at ``target`` not as regular "
"runtime code, but directly as initcode. The ``*args`` are interpreted as "
"constructor arguments, and are ABI-encoded and included when executing the "
"initcode."
msgstr ""
"將 ``target`` 的程式碼複製到記憶體中並作為 initcode 執行。換句話說，此操作將 "
"``target`` 處的程式碼不是作為常規執行時期程式碼，而是直接作為 initcode 來解"
"釋。``*args`` 被解釋為建構函數引數，並在執行 initcode 時進行 ABI 編碼並包含在"
"內。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:120
msgid "``target``: Address of the blueprint to invoke"
msgstr "``target``：要呼叫的藍圖合約位址"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:121 ../../../built-in-functions.rst:164
msgid "``*args``: Constructor arguments to forward to the initcode."
msgstr "``*args``：要轉發給 initcode 的建構函數引數。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:123
msgid ""
"``raw_args``: If ``True``, ``*args`` must be a single ``Bytes[...]`` "
"argument, which will be interpreted as a raw bytes buffer to forward to the "
"create operation (which is useful for instance, if pre- ABI-encoded data is "
"passed in from elsewhere). (Optional, default ``False``)"
msgstr ""
"``raw_args``：如果為 ``True``，``*args`` 必須是單個 ``Bytes[...]`` 引數，將被"
"解讀為要轉發給建立操作的原始位元組緩衝區（例如，當從其他地方傳入預先 ABI 編碼"
"的資料時很有用）。（選用，默認 ``False``）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:124
msgid ""
"``code_offset``: The offset to start the ``EXTCODECOPY`` from (Optional, "
"default 3)"
msgstr "``code_offset``：開始 ``EXTCODECOPY`` 的偏移量（選用，默認 3）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:128
msgid ""
"Returns the address of the created contract. If the create operation fails "
"(for instance, in the case of a ``CREATE2`` collision), execution will "
"revert. If ``code_offset >= target.codesize`` (ex. if there is no code at "
"``target``), execution will revert."
msgstr ""
"回傳建立的合約的位址。如果建立操作失敗（例如在 ``CREATE2`` 衝突的情況下），執"
"行將會還原。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:130
msgid ""
"@external\n"
"def foo(blueprint: address) -> address:\n"
"    arg1: uint256 = 18\n"
"    arg2: String[32] = \"some string\"\n"
"    return create_from_blueprint(blueprint, arg1, arg2, code_offset=1)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:140
msgid ""
"To properly deploy a blueprint contract, special deploy bytecode must be "
"used. The output of ``vyper -f blueprint_bytecode`` will produce bytecode "
"which deploys an ERC-5202 compatible blueprint."
msgstr ""
"要正確部署藍圖合約，必須使用特殊的部署位元組碼。``vyper -f "
"blueprint_bytecode`` 的輸出將產生部署 ERC-5202 相容藍圖的位元組碼。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:144
msgid ""
"Prior to Vyper version ``0.4.0``, the ``code_offset`` parameter defaulted to "
"``0``."
msgstr "在 Vyper ``0.4.0`` 版之前，``code_offset`` 參數默認為 ``0``。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:148
msgid ""
"It is recommended to deploy blueprints with an `ERC-5202 <https://eips."
"ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-5202>`_ preamble like ``0xFE7100`` to guard them from "
"being called as regular contracts. This is particularly important for "
"factories where the constructor has side effects (including "
"``SELFDESTRUCT``!), as those could get executed by *anybody* calling the "
"blueprint contract directly. The ``code_offset=`` kwarg is provided (and "
"defaults to the ERC-5202 default of 3) to enable this pattern:"
msgstr ""
"建議使用 `ERC-5202 <https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-5202>`_ 前導碼（如 "
"``0xFE7100``）來部署藍圖，以防止它們被當作常規合約呼叫。這對於建構函數有副作"
"用（包括 ``SELFDESTRUCT``！）的工廠特別重要，因為這些副作用可能會被*任何人*直"
"接呼叫藍圖合約而執行。提供了 ``code_offset=`` 關鍵字引數（默認為 ERC-5202 的"
"默認值 3）以啟用此模式："

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:150
msgid ""
"@external\n"
"def foo(blueprint: address) -> address:\n"
"    # `blueprint` is a blueprint contract with some known preamble b\"abcd..."
"\"\n"
"    return create_from_blueprint(blueprint, code_offset=<preamble length>)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:160
msgid ""
"Create a contract using the given ``initcode``. Provides low-level access to "
"the ``CREATE`` and ``CREATE2`` opcodes."
msgstr ""
"使用給定的 ``initcode`` 建立合約。提供對 ``CREATE`` 和 ``CREATE2`` 操作碼的低"
"階存取。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:162
msgid "``initcode``: Initcode bytes"
msgstr "``initcode``：Initcode 位元組"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:168
msgid ""
"Returns the address of the created contract. If the create operation fails "
"(for instance, in the case of a ``CREATE2`` collision), execution will "
"revert."
msgstr ""
"回傳建立的合約的位址。如果建立操作失敗（例如在 ``CREATE2`` 衝突的情況下），執"
"行將會還原。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:170
msgid ""
"@external\n"
"def foo() -> address:\n"
"    # create the bytes of an empty vyper contract\n"
"    return "
"raw_create(x\"0x61000361000f6000396100036000f35f5ffd855820cd372fb85148700fa88095e3492d3f9f5beb43e555e5ff26d95f5a6adc36f8e6038000a1657679706572830004020033\")"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:180
msgid "Call to the specified Ethereum address."
msgstr "呼叫指定的以太坊位址。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:182
msgid "``to``: Destination address to call to"
msgstr "``to``：要呼叫的目標位址"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:183
msgid "``data``: Data to send to the destination address"
msgstr "``data``：要發送到目標位址的資料"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:184
msgid ""
"``max_outsize``: Maximum length of the bytes array returned from the call. "
"If the returned call data exceeds this length, only this number of bytes is "
"returned. (Optional, default ``0``)"
msgstr ""
"``max_outsize``：從呼叫回傳的位元組陣列的最大長度。如果回傳的呼叫資料超過此長"
"度，則只回傳此數量的位元組。（選用，默認 ``0``）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:185
msgid ""
"``gas``: The amount of gas to attach to the call. (Optional, defaults to "
"``msg.gas``)."
msgstr "``gas``：附加到呼叫的 gas 數量。（選用，默認為 ``msg.gas``）。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:186
msgid ""
"``value``: The wei value to send to the address (Optional, default ``0``)"
msgstr "``value``：要發送到該位址的 wei 值（選用，默認 ``0``）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:187
msgid ""
"``is_delegate_call``: If ``True``, the call will be sent as ``DELEGATECALL`` "
"(Optional, default ``False``)"
msgstr ""
"``is_delegate_call``：如果為 ``True``，呼叫將作為 ``DELEGATECALL`` 發送（選"
"用，默認 ``False``）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:188
msgid ""
"``is_static_call``: If ``True``, the call will be sent as ``STATICCALL`` "
"(Optional, default ``False``)"
msgstr ""
"``is_static_call``：如果為 ``True``，呼叫將作為 ``STATICCALL`` 發送（選用，默"
"認 ``False``）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:189
msgid ""
"``revert_on_failure``: If ``True``, the call will revert on a failure, "
"otherwise ``success`` will be returned (Optional, default ``True``)"
msgstr ""
"``revert_on_failure``：如果為 ``True``，呼叫將在失敗時還原，否則將回傳 "
"``success``（選用，默認 ``True``）"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:193
msgid ""
"Returns the data returned by the call as a ``Bytes`` list, with "
"``max_outsize`` as the max length. The actual size of the returned data may "
"be less than ``max_outsize``. You can use ``len`` to obtain the actual size."
msgstr ""
"將呼叫回傳的資料作為 ``Bytes`` 列表回傳，``max_outsize`` 為最大長度。回傳資料"
"的實際大小可能小於 ``max_outsize``。你可以使用 ``len`` 來取得實際大小。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:195
msgid "Returns nothing if ``max_outsize`` is omitted or set to ``0``."
msgstr "如果省略 ``max_outsize`` 或設為 ``0``，則不回傳任何內容。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:197
msgid ""
"Returns ``success`` in a tuple with return value if ``revert_on_failure`` is "
"set to ``False``."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``revert_on_failure`` 設為 ``False``，則在元組中回傳 ``success`` 以及回"
"傳值。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:199
msgid ""
"@external\n"
"@payable\n"
"def foo(_target: address) -> Bytes[32]:\n"
"    response: Bytes[32] = raw_call(_target, method_id(\"someMethodName()\"), "
"max_outsize=32, value=msg.value)\n"
"    return response\n"
"\n"
"@external\n"
"@payable\n"
"def bar(_target: address) -> Bytes[32]:\n"
"    success: bool = False\n"
"    response: Bytes[32] = b\"\"\n"
"    x: uint256 = 123\n"
"    success, response = raw_call(\n"
"        _target,\n"
"        abi_encode(x, method_id=method_id(\"someMethodName(uint256)\")),\n"
"        max_outsize=32,\n"
"        value=msg.value,\n"
"        revert_on_failure=False\n"
"        )\n"
"    assert success\n"
"    return response"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:225
msgid ""
"Regarding \"forwarding all gas\", note that, while Vyper will provide ``msg."
"gas`` to the call, in practice, there are some subtleties around forwarding "
"all remaining gas on the EVM which are out of scope of this documentation "
"and could be subject to change. For instance, see the language in EIP-150 "
"around \"all but one 64th\"."
msgstr ""
"關於「轉送所有 gas」，請注意，雖然 Vyper 會向呼叫提供 ``msg.gas``，但實際上"
"在 EVM 上轉送所有剩餘 gas 存在一些細微之處，這些超出了本文件的範圍且可能會有"
"變更。例如，請參閱 EIP-150 中關於「all but one 64th」的說明。"

#: ../../../built-in-functions.rst:229
msgid ""
"Provides low level access to the ``LOG`` opcodes, emitting a log without "
